Purpose *    To promote education and exchange of information concerning data, analytics, and artificial intelligence within the meaning of Section 501(c)(6) of the Internal Revenue Code of 1986, as amended.   *   To establish channels for the education and communication of information to and from members in the field of artificial intelligence, data, and analytics.   *   To conduct conferences, meetings, discussion groups, forums, panels, lectures, and other programs concerned with developing and exchanging information among members.   *   To encourage and strengthen the participation of all qualified members.   *   To promote the acceptance of artificial intelligence and other best data practices.   *   To encourage the development of products embedding and using artificial intelligence, data, and analytics.   *   To provide a forum for the promotion of excellence in information processing by recognizing those individuals who, judged by their peers, put forth the highest effort and ethical standards and succeed in best-utilizing data, analytics, and artificial intelligence within their organizations.   *   To provide a safe and unbiased way of discussing the ethical ramifications of the use of artificial intelligence, data, and analytics across a broad range of industries and humanity.

Description: This functional beverage has its origin in eastern Asia about 2,500 years ago.
Full Description: This functional beverage has its origin in eastern Asia about 2,500 years ago. Kombucha originated in Northeast China (historically referred to as Manchuria) around 220 B.C. and was initially prized for its healing properties. Its name is reportedly derived from Dr. Kombu, a Korean physician who brought the fermented tea to Japan as a curative for Emperor Inkyo. Eventually the tea was brought to Europe as a result of trade route expansions in the early 20th century, most notably appearing in Russia (as “Kambucha”) and Germany (as “Kombuchaschwamm”). But, Kombucha is much more than just a fermented tea product. It is a lifestyle, or at least, a life choice that many people note as life changing on some level. Most people start drinking Kombucha because it makes them feel good and many experience an improvement in health; unfortunately formal research is scarce.

Description: The Worlds Number One Doggy Dating App and 'Social Pet-Work'
Full Description: Dogs get Lonely Without Furry Friends & New App Woofr Makes it Easy for Pooches to Connect and hopefully Help Their Humans Find Love Too! Experts agree that dogs are naturally pack animals, so even with a loving owner, they are often are missing something when not being able to be around fellow-four legged friends. The new app Woofr makes it easy for owners to link up and arrange doggie fun or even date days, love could be in the air for pooches and people alike! While a dog may be a man (or woman's) best friend, this still doesn't change the fact that their nature, as pack animals, is to want to spend time bonding with fellow canines. Did you know that there are over 500 million pet dogs globally, plus 1 in 5 has a social media account?!! Furthermore many people face the problem of not having access to another dog or dogs for their beloved pet to play and bond with, a solution was definitely needed. Answering the call, is what some are calling the “World's First Doggy Dating App” Woofr, a fun mobile app (‘social petwork’ if you will) that allows users to show off their pets to make connections with other local dog owners and arrange doggy play sessions, that will likely help their pets be more happy and healthy, and who knows, love could be on the cards for the owners too! The app is available for free on iOS and is coming soon on Android. So there may be just a bit of doggy romance or at least new friendships in the air for both hounds and humans. “When it comes to making connections swiping left or right has become an integral part of the dating experience for many people,” commented James Gaubert, from Woofr. “Now we've opened the door for pet people to use the same kind of cool and convenient technology to find BFF's for their beloved pooches, and maybe even a little love for themselves, something which everyone is sure to enjoy and appreciate, Woofr is the dating app that puts hounds first and humans second”. https://apple.co/2Kz1t0O

Description: CompanyTRAK uses true Contact Tracing and Social Distancing, helping companies bring employees back to work in a safe environment.
Full Description: Built from the ground up to be a true Contact Tracing, Social Distancing solution, CompanyTRAK uses patent pending technology to follow and log interaction of employees.  Mobile location services (GPS) and BLE technologies, Bluetooth (BT) tags and locators and/or Ultra-Wideband (UWB) devices. Our enterprise platform includes the following solutions through web and mobile applications, Bluetooth locators, tags and UWB wearables: 1. Daily Employee Health Questionnaire 2. Contact Tracing 3. Social Distancing 4. Visitor Questionnaire & Tracing System 5. CT Portal – Corporate Admin & Reporting CompanyTRAK traces primary exposure and notifies employees and assigned HR/Admin when another employee that they have been in contact with self-reports with symptoms or with positive test results. Employees start the day with their Daily Questionnaire prior to entering the building.  All submitted info is sent to HR/Admin in the CT Portal.  As employees enter the Geofenced building, the solution starts tracing their interaction with other employees.  If they come within the 6-foot proximity of each other, they are alerted through LED lights and vibration, and their contact is logged in the CT Portal.  If any of their contacts report symptoms or a positive test result in the next 14-18 days, a notification is sent to them and HR/Admin about a possible risk of exposure.   HR/Admins have access to the CT Portal through various roles.  This helps authorized personnel to manage employees with their Daily PPE/Questionnaire and temperature checks that employees need to follow. HR/Admins are provided access to maintain and edit employees, locations, equipment, and reporting.  Authorized HR/Admins will have access to edit the status of employees.  If an employee recovers from the virus, HR/Admin has the ability to reset their status to Safe after receiving their updated test results. All of this is controlled through integration and APIs in the CT Portal.  From customizing the mobile app and extension URLs, to running reports on employee surveys and status, the CT Portal provide HR and Admins the ability to manage their companies and minimize possible risk of exposure within their employee base.

Full Description: EAAT uses bioprinting technology to produce sustainable fish products for human consumption. EAAT has acquired the exclusive rights to use and modify the intellectual property of the global leader in live cell printing for the manufacture and sale of bioprinted fish and meat. Initially, with this technology, and our expertise and experience, we will sustainably produce and sell lab-grown, non-GMO, edible and marketable fish protein. EAAT will ultimately manufacture consumable fish and meat products with minimal waste, without contaminants and without depleting the worlds’ natural resources or destroying its environment. EAAT’S proprietary bioprinting technology is currently the most precise on the market. The design and features of EAAT's bioprinter provide the flexibility necessary to manufacture our end product successfully and achieve our scaling timeline. Today, there are a few different 3D cell printers commercially available responding to a rising demand for live cell printing, for customizable live cell arrays, tissue bio-fabrication/bioprinting research and other applications. EAAT’s proprietary technology offers the only 3D cell printer on the market with 95% live cell viability, whereas other bioprinters typically print at less than 50% viability. It can also print up to 16 channels at once, providing the ability to print all cell lines, media and other materials at once. EAAT’s ability to control all aspects of production through the vertical integration of its supply chain, coupled with the ability to print cells at a faster rate and with greater viability, and its already established distribution network, provides EAAT with a significant advantage over its potential competitors.

Description: The Future of Baby Products
Full Description: The Babyfi Hollow Headrest is a safe and comfortable headrest for babies from 0 to 6 months old. It is ergonomically designed to reduce pressure on the head and neck, and it is made from breathable, non-toxic materials. The headrest is machine washable and is recommended by US licensed pediatricians. It is a perfect gift for a baby shower or newborn registry. Babyfi Key Differentiators: Breathability - The hollow design of the headrest allows for maximum air circulation, minimizing the risk of suffocation. The 100% organic muslin cotton casing has a wide weave and is fully breathable. Comfort and Health - The headrest is designed to evenly distribute weight and reduce pressure on the baby's head. It has a 7.6-degree incline that complies with federal regulations. The mesh materials gently cradle the baby's head and allow for proper air circulation, reducing sweating and irritation. Certified Safety - We have a Children Product Certificate in line with consumer product safety requirements outlined by the U.S. Consumer Product Safety Commission. Products are tested by a U.S. Consumer Product Safety Commission approved lab. Unlike other infant pillows that are now banned because of breathing obstructing materials or high incline levels, our product does NOT fall under any Federal bans. Non-Toxic - This is a hypoallergenic, food grade product with no latex, glue, foam, chemicals, biocides, fire retardants or allergens used in it or its construction. Zero Waste - Crafted from 100% recyclable, biodegradable materials. The elegant packaging, also 100% recyclable and biodegradable, serves as a high-quality storage box for baby essentials like bibs, pacifiers, and toys. Washable - Sanitize and clean away spit up, milk, bacteria and more for a fresh, hygienic naptime. This product is machine washable in cold water.
